’Ł@0c0566ee31f6a4f36e40607acafc9d484fed37e6a9c34e8eb8203505f007c3afŚģTitle: title: random int
Path: Examples
Content:
Generate a non-negative random integer.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random int


```
Generate a random integer between 0 (inclusive) and 500 (inclusive).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random int ..500


```
Generate a random integer greater than or equal to 100000.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random int 100000..


```
Generate a random integer between -10 (inclusive) and 10 (inclusive).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random int (-10)..10


```
